import React from 'react';
import { Button, Segment, Grid, Header, Icon } from 'semantic-ui-react';


const MainSegment = () => {
    return (
        <React.Fragment>
            <Segment inverted>
                <Grid columns="equal" black>
                    <Grid.Row textAlign='center'>
                        <Grid.Column>
                            <Segment black inverted>
                                1
                        </Segment>
                        </Grid.Column>
                        <Grid.Column>
                            <Segment color='red' inverted>
                                2
                    </Segment>
                        </Grid.Column>
                        <Grid.Column>
                            <Segment color='red' inverted>
                                3
                    </Segment>
                        </Grid.Column>
                    </Grid.Row>
                </Grid>
            </Segment>
        </React.Fragment>
    )
}

export default MainSegment;
